<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Buckingham" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Buckingham,</orth> 1) county of England: <bibl n="shak. 3h6 4.8.14" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C IV, 8, 14</bibl>. 2) <emph>Duke Humphrey of B.,</emph> a) <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.1.69" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 1, 69</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.1.69" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 1, 69</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.3.72" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 3, 72</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.3.72" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 3, 72</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.4.58" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 4, 58</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 2.1.165" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 165</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.8.20" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 8, 20</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 5.1.15" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 15</bibl> etc. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 1.1.10" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C I, 1, 10</bibl>. b) <cit><quote>Henry Duke of B.</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.17" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 3, 17</bibl></cit> etc. etc. <bibl n="shak. h8 2.1.107" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 II, 1, 107</bibl>. alluded to: <bibl n="shak. h8 1.2.195" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 2, 195</bibl>. c) the son of the latter: <bibl n="shak. h8 1.1.115" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 I, 1, 115</bibl>. 199 etc. <bibl n="shak. h8 3.2.256" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 256</bibl>.
